data.description: Welcome to your new home! As you drive in to the tastefully decorated driveway, you’ll love walking by the manicured lawn and through the relaxing screened front patio to the welcoming double door entrance. This incredibly upgraded home is move-in ready and sold FULLY FURNISHED inside the highly sought-after 55+ community of Plantation at Leesburg. This lovely property is tucked away on the north end of the neighborhood for easy entrance/exit. Boasting nearly 1,900 square feet of beautifully furnished living space, this 2-car garage home features two large bedrooms, two full bathrooms, a formal dining area, a Florida room with a relaxing view of the fire-pit in the large back yard. Enjoy the valuable maintenance-free gutters, equipped with 'leaf guards'. As you step inside, you will be immediately greeted by newly installed flooring throughout, fresh blue-grey paint, high vaulted ceilings, and an abundance of natural light that shines through the expanded windows in the front and rear of the home. Both bathrooms have new counters lovely vessel sinks. The large upgraded kitchen is adjacent to the indoor washer/dryer room and opens to one of TWO LIVING ROOMS. Seamlessly enter the central-air lanai after dinner through additional sliding doors. The kitchen has been immaculately updated with brand new stainless steel appliances and features ample counter and cabinet space for all of your cooking and hosting needs. In this truly beautiful home, you will enjoy the perfection of luxury living in an safe and peaceful community that offers every imaginable convenience and amenity. Those who enjoy golf will find everything you need within the community's two 18-hole semi-private golf courses, which have two PGA professional assistants on staff. Residents of this exclusive community have access to three fully equipped clubhouses, three sparkling swimming pools, an on-site restaurant, dance floor, theatre stage, fishing ponds, and more activities than you’ll have time to do! Be prepared to fall in love with this move-in ready home! Schedule a showing to see this beauty. **WASHER/DRYER INCLUDED**
